data.description: LUXURIOUS LIVING IN STATELY BEAUVOIR…..This craftsman home features a welcoming 41 ft porch and upgrades throughout!  This 3BD/2BA home offers an office, greatroom with stoned fireplace & gas logs, custom bookshelves. The Chef's Kitchen with custom soft close cabinets & drawers with organizers/dividers, adjustable shelving, granite countertops, farmhouse sink, stainless steel Kitchen Aid appliances include a semipro gas cooktop, electric oven & microwave.   10' x 4 ' breakfast bar/ dining that will seat 6-8. Take advantage of the dedicated beverage station with plenty of storage - 22 drawers in the kitchen + under the bar deep cabinets for additional  storage. The living quarters offer 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 spa-like baths. The guest bath offers a soaking tub, all tile / rectangular sink, Granite countertops, tall toilets with "soft close" lid. Ceiling fans in every room including the primary bath/dressing area. The primary bath has  5ft x 5ft walk in shower with custom bench & shower niche.  All LED lights throughout, spray foam insulation & floored attic. Garage has lift to easily store items in attic. (lift holds up to 250 lbs!) ADT security with mobile app feature to set remotely. Smoke detectors & carbon monoxide detectors throughout. Water heater has circulating line allowing water to heat INSTANTLY throughout! Dehumidifier is attic. The exterior of the home features hardiboard siding, a Hunter sprinkler system with wireless rain sensor. Epoxy covered interlocked flextile garage floor.  Storage/Utility space heated & cooled off garage. 3 " plantation shutters throughout. You must see this home to believe the upgraded features! Schedule your tour TODAY!
